Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: The snow of 1996, 1947 and 1888
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p00yjw4k
Last Broadcast Date: Fri 12 Jan 1996
The New York blizzard of 1996, the great snowfall of 1947 and the "paralysing anxiety" during the blizzard of 1888, as chronicled by Alistair Cooke.